WEBVTT

00:04.689 --> 00:08.712
God bless you.

00:19.108 --> 00:25.440
I’m sitting here this afternoon
with Shri Mataji Nirmala Devi.

00:25.440 --> 00:26.902
Is that how I say your name,
Shri Mataji?

00:26.902 --> 00:27.600
That’s correct, it’s correct.

00:29.120 --> 00:32.360
Shri Mataji is a world-renowned
spiritual leader,

00:32.360 --> 00:34.840
and we’re very happy to welcome
you here today.

00:34.840 --> 00:35.440
Thank you very much.

00:36.640 --> 00:41.000
Shri Mataji. Can you tell us
when you first realized

00:41.000 --> 00:44.280
that you had this
special spiritual gift?

00:48.560 --> 00:51.400
You see, it’s like this,
that when we are born

00:51.400 --> 00:53.440
as human beings,
we know we are human beings.

00:53.440 --> 00:56.400
In the same way, I knew
from my very birth

00:56.400 --> 00:59.400
that I was something of that kind.

01:01.200 --> 01:05.480
And since you’ve been a young person,
you’ve been spreading

01:05.480 --> 01:10.200
this spiritual message,
or is this something that

01:10.200 --> 01:12.120
you’ve just recently begun to do?

01:12.920 --> 01:17.000
No, I had to wait and see
certain things about human beings.

01:17.840 --> 01:21.160
Because I had to study
why human beings cannot get

01:21.160 --> 01:25.520
Realization en masse.
They should get it en masse,

01:25.520 --> 01:29.200
otherwise, if one person gets it,
then people don’t understand them.

01:29.200 --> 01:32.480
They crucify them, they poison them,
they’ve tortured them.

01:33.120 --> 01:37.720
So why shouldn’t it work out en masse?
And so, I had to study

01:37.720 --> 01:41.080
for years together.
At the age of my 47th year,

01:41.600 --> 01:47.280
I discovered a method by which
Self-realization can be

01:47.280 --> 01:49.040
achieved en masse.

01:49.800 --> 01:53.000
Shri Mataji, you use the term
Self-realization.

01:53.000 --> 01:56.560
That’s a term we’re not really
very familiar with here in America.

01:56.560 --> 01:58.040
Can you explain that to me?

01:59.200 --> 02:02.360
It’s the same as what Christ has said
that, “You are to be born again”.

02:04.200 --> 02:08.800
That is when, like a bird, you see,
you are an egg,

02:08.800 --> 02:13.320
and then you become a bird.
And also a bird is called a

02:13.320 --> 02:17.640
‘twice-born’ in Sanskrit language.
In the same way, a human being

02:18.160 --> 02:21.280
is bound by his conditioning,
by his ego,

02:22.280 --> 02:28.520
but when he is born again,
then he is called as a

02:28.520 --> 02:32.680
Self-realized person,
because he knows about himself,

02:32.680 --> 02:36.280
about his inner being.
And also he’s endowed

02:36.280 --> 02:40.360
on his central nervous system
with a new awareness

02:40.880 --> 02:45.200
that Jung had described as
Collective Consciousness.

02:46.120 --> 02:50.880
So it’s not just a certificate
one can give that you are baptized,

02:50.880 --> 02:54.720
or you are Self-realized,
or you are twice-born.

02:55.440 --> 03:00.280
It’s a living process,
which is the last breakthrough

03:00.280 --> 03:06.120
in your awareness, where you become;
it’s a question of becoming.

03:06.120 --> 03:11.360
You become a personality
which can feel the

03:11.360 --> 03:15.480
All-pervading Power,
about which every scripture

03:15.480 --> 03:18.920
has described,
on your central nervous system.

03:19.640 --> 03:23.360
This is what we call as ‘bodh’,
as in Buddha,

03:23.880 --> 03:28.360
called as ‘Veda’, as in Veda.
Means you have to know it

03:28.360 --> 03:32.640
on your central nervous system,
on your fingertips,

03:32.640 --> 03:35.520
as Mohammed Sahib has said that,
“You have to know it

03:35.520 --> 03:39.560
on your fingertips”
that it exists all around you,

03:39.560 --> 03:44.880
like a very beautiful, soothing,
cool breeze.

03:45.600 --> 03:47.680
This is the cool breeze
of the Holy Ghost.

03:48.720 --> 03:51.760
So Shri Mataji,
what you are describing then,

03:51.760 --> 03:56.120
is a process that comes from
inside each of us,

03:56.120 --> 03:58.080
and is something that
everyone can feel,

03:58.080 --> 03:59.400
or just a few people?

03:59.960 --> 04:03.320
No, everybody can feel.
‘Sahaja’, you see,

04:03.320 --> 04:07.560
we call it a Sahaja Yoga.
Sahaja means born with you.

04:08.200 --> 04:15.960
It is born with you, this yoga,
or we can say this promise of yoga

04:15.960 --> 04:18.440
is born with you.
It means there is a power within you,

04:19.640 --> 04:22.400
which is called in Sanskrit language
as Kundalini,

04:23.120 --> 04:27.400
which resides in the triangular bone,
which, surprisingly,

04:28.240 --> 04:32.880
the Greeks called as sacrum bone.
That means they knew it’s a sacred bone.

04:32.880 --> 04:35.800
And this is the fourth power
which resides within us,

04:37.280 --> 04:43.720
and which somehow or other awakened,
pierces through your fontanel bone area,

04:44.240 --> 04:52.360
and you really get the experience
of actualization of your second birth,

04:52.360 --> 04:57.400
by feeling the cool breeze
coming out of your head, you yourself.

04:57.400 --> 05:00.640
And you can experience it
on your fingertips.

05:00.640 --> 05:04.480
It’s not just imagination.
You have to certify yourself.

05:06.040 --> 05:09.160
Well Shri Mataji,
It sounds extremely simple.

05:09.720 --> 05:13.920
How does one have this feeling
coming from their fingertips,

05:13.920 --> 05:16.960
and a cool breeze coming
from the top of the head?

05:16.960 --> 05:24.440
Everything vital has to be simple.
See how a seed sprouts.

05:24.440 --> 05:26.120
They have to just put it
in the Mother Earth.

05:26.640 --> 05:29.720
The Mother Earth has got the capacity
to sprout it,

05:30.240 --> 05:34.480
and the seed has all the
built-in machinery in it.

05:34.480 --> 05:37.440
In the same way, you too have
everything within you,

05:37.440 --> 05:38.480
and it just sprouts.

05:39.560 --> 05:44.360
So Shri Mataji,
once this is sprouted, then what?

05:44.360 --> 05:47.480
What happens to me?
Do I become different?

05:48.160 --> 05:53.200
You start transforming completely,
because you get the light.

05:54.080 --> 05:56.880
When there is no light,
you can catch hold of a snake

05:56.880 --> 05:59.920
thinking it’s a rope.
But when there’s light,

05:59.920 --> 06:04.640
you can see it yourself and you drop it.
So you can see the saints,

06:05.600 --> 06:08.520
who are real saints,
incarnations, prophets,

06:08.520 --> 06:12.160
they never committed mistakes.
We might think they committed mistakes

06:12.160 --> 06:14.560
because our knowledge about them
is limited.

06:15.400 --> 06:18.160
But they never committed mistakes,
they never committed sins,

06:18.720 --> 06:23.040
because they were connected
with the Divine Power,

06:23.040 --> 06:24.680
because they were Self-realized.

06:26.200 --> 06:29.280
Well, the transforming power
that you describe, then,

06:29.280 --> 06:33.880
is something that once it happens to me,
I keep it for myself.

06:33.880 --> 06:38.600
Can I give this transformation power
to my friends or my relatives?

06:38.600 --> 06:40.000
Or is it just mine?

06:40.000 --> 06:43.600
No, no, of course.
A light which is lightened

06:43.600 --> 06:46.520
is not kept under the table,
as Christ has told.

06:46.520 --> 06:48.720
In the same way,
when you are enlightened,

06:48.720 --> 06:52.240
you can enlighten other people.
You are endowed with that power.

06:52.240 --> 06:54.720
You have those powers,
then you can do it.

06:55.920 --> 07:00.440
Because it passes through
your seven subtle, six subtle centres,

07:01.080 --> 07:07.880
and pierces through your last center
of limbic area, which is nourished,

07:09.040 --> 07:17.320
which is being made knowledgeable.
So when you start giving this to others,

07:17.320 --> 07:21.720
you can feel the centres of other people
on your fingertips,

07:21.720 --> 07:26.280
and you know what is their problem.
Only thing, if you have to know,

07:26.280 --> 07:32.440
only if you can know,
how to get rid of those obstacles

07:32.440 --> 07:35.560
of these subtle centres,
you can manage it.

08:30.400 --> 08:32.960
I think that’s what Americans
would worry,

08:32.960 --> 08:36.560
whether they would just become a nation
of very passive people.

08:37.320 --> 08:40.520
That is not the case then
with this meditation technique?

08:40.520 --> 08:42.480
Not at all.
You become very dynamic.

08:43.280 --> 08:48.240
You see, actually, you are passive
when you are afraid of something,

08:48.240 --> 08:51.040
when you don’t know anything.
Then you become passive.

08:51.680 --> 08:54.640
But you become dynamic
when you know everything,

08:55.160 --> 08:58.040
and you know you are not doing
anything wrong,

08:58.040 --> 08:59.800
so you are not afraid of anything.

09:01.160 --> 09:05.560
Shri Mataji,
in the background information we received,

09:05.560 --> 09:10.960
I know you’ve travelled around the world
for several years, 19 or 20,

09:11.560 --> 09:15.360
and you’ve been spreading this message.
When you came to America,

09:15.360 --> 09:19.560
I believe it was in the early 1970s.
You came at that time

09:19.560 --> 09:23.320
with not only this message,
but a message about false gurus.

09:23.840 --> 09:27.200
And in the 1980s,
you warned us again

09:27.200 --> 09:33.360
that we needed the Self-realization,
and that AIDS was on the horizon.

09:33.360 --> 09:37.040
Is there a message that you have for us
for the 1990s?

09:37.040 --> 09:40.160
What’s the use?
Even if I tell you, people won’t listen.

09:40.960 --> 09:44.320
I’ve told them about AIDS.
I’ve told them about a kind

09:44.320 --> 09:49.280
of a paralysis of the conscious mind.
That’s working out already.

09:49.280 --> 09:55.480
Also about very speedy people,
very speedy children,

09:56.040 --> 09:59.680
but they don’t listen.
The trouble of Americans is this,

09:59.680 --> 10:05.480
that they think everything is money.
And those who make them pay,

10:05.480 --> 10:09.840
or those whom they can purchase
with money, they listen to them.

10:10.880 --> 10:12.640
If Christ was here,
they would not have listened

10:12.640 --> 10:15.960
to Him either,
because you cannot purchase Christ,

10:15.960 --> 10:20.360
you cannot purchase Me.
So those who can make money,

10:20.360 --> 10:26.760
those who can make business
out of all this, then they will listen.

10:26.760 --> 10:34.000
And those who really know the job,
those who really know the Divine Power,

10:35.200 --> 10:40.360
those who are honest,
will never take any money for this,

10:40.360 --> 10:42.040
because you cannot pay for it.

10:43.240 --> 10:46.240
Well, that brings me to the New Age,
Shri Mataji.

10:46.240 --> 10:50.160
Here in America, we’re very involved
in the so-called New Age

10:50.160 --> 10:54.440
of Enlightenment.
We invest in crystals,

10:54.440 --> 10:59.920
we invest in channelling sessions,
we have exotic diets, we jog.

11:01.120 --> 11:06.560
How does Sahaja Yoga differ
from the other New Age phenomena

11:06.560 --> 11:07.320
that we’re seeing?

11:07.320 --> 11:12.640
It’s all artificial things.
Artificiality is not going to give you

11:12.640 --> 11:16.600
that personality which comes
through inner transformation.

11:17.920 --> 11:20.680
And that’s why this yoga,
this union with the Divine,

11:20.680 --> 11:24.840
has to be established.
Now supposing if a tree is sick,

11:24.840 --> 11:28.000
and we try to put some ointment
on its leaves,

11:28.000 --> 11:31.880
do you think the tree will be cured?
We have to go to the roots.

11:31.880 --> 11:34.640
In the same way,
we have to go to the roots.

11:34.640 --> 11:38.240
And Sahaja Yoga deals with your roots,
not with your outside.

11:38.960 --> 11:41.640
I see. You mentioned money,
Shri Mataji.

11:41.640 --> 11:43.960
And of course,
many people are getting rich

11:43.960 --> 11:48.040
with the New Age seminars,
and New Age books and crystals,

11:48.040 --> 11:53.600
and other paraphernalia.
Sahaja Yoga does cost money, doesn’t it?

11:53.600 --> 11:55.900
No, it does not at all.
You cannot pay for it.

11:55.900 --> 11:58.760
It does not cost you money.
Of course, I mean, supposing

11:58.760 --> 12:02.240
you have to come and see me here,
you have to pay for the taxi, that’s all.

12:03.760 --> 12:05.480
I’m not supposed to pay for that.

12:09.360 --> 12:13.080
And that’s all? That’s the only cost,
just whatever cost you incur

12:13.080 --> 12:15.360
in getting the message?

12:15.360 --> 12:19.320
Of course.
Because this is a living process.

12:20.320 --> 12:22.720
And anything living
does not understand money.

12:22.720 --> 12:30.960
I see. Shri Mataji, here in America,
we have what many people view

12:30.960 --> 12:35.040
as two separate societies.
We have a society on the one hand

12:35.040 --> 12:41.960
that is very affluent, very wealthy,
technological advancements.

12:43.000 --> 12:47.120
And then on the other hand,
we have an America that is impoverished

12:47.120 --> 12:51.200
morally, socially.
We have crimes and child abuse.

12:53.600 --> 12:57.800
What is the explanation for these
two separate Americas existing

12:57.800 --> 13:00.600
at the same time?
And how can we get rid of

13:00.600 --> 13:04.200
those negative aspects
that are becoming so prominent

13:04.200 --> 13:05.280
in American life?

13:05.880 --> 13:10.320
There’s imbalance in life.
They are completely imbalanced people,

13:10.320 --> 13:14.280
because they run after money.
Hook or crook, get money.

13:14.280 --> 13:17.760
Do what you like.
Women think that even selling

13:17.760 --> 13:20.760
their chastity is all right
because you get money.

13:20.760 --> 13:25.480
“What’s wrong?” They can sell everything.
So there’s no sense of morality

13:25.480 --> 13:28.760
within them.
And that’s why all these things start.

13:28.760 --> 13:32.480
For example, drugs do not come
from the people who are addicted to drugs,

13:32.480 --> 13:36.360
but the ones who sell drugs.
They sell drugs because they get money.

13:36.360 --> 13:40.440
They are not bothered as to
how many people they are ruining by that.

13:40.440 --> 13:42.920
So, it’s a money orientation
in everything.

13:42.920 --> 13:51.280
It’s an extreme behaviour towards money.
Money has its own place

13:51.280 --> 13:54.840
and it should be treated
in its own limitations and understanding.

13:55.680 --> 14:01.600
So when you go headlong
with this idea of getting money,

14:01.600 --> 14:06.920
you enter into all these blind alleys
where you get lost.

14:07.920 --> 14:10.280
Well, are you a socialist Shri Mataji?

14:10.280 --> 14:13.720
I’m not a socialist,
nor am I a capitalist, but I’m both.

14:14.760 --> 14:17.680
Because I have all the capital,
because I have the powers,

14:18.200 --> 14:22.320
and I’m a socialist because I can’t live
without distributing it.

14:23.960 --> 14:30.400
And that’s what you do on a daily basis.
When we talk about transformation,

14:30.400 --> 14:34.160
Shri Mataji, many of us look
at our planet Earth

14:34.160 --> 14:40.040
and see the ecological changes,
the disasters, all over the world.

14:40.640 --> 14:43.320
Here in America, one moment
we have drought

14:43.320 --> 14:48.680
and the next moment we have flooding.
Is that also part of this imbalance?

14:48.680 --> 14:54.840
Absolutely. Absolutely.
You see, we have to know that machinery

14:54.840 --> 14:57.640
or technology is for us.
We are not for them.

14:58.800 --> 15:02.080
There has to be a balance of how far
to go with machinery

15:03.000 --> 15:07.920
and how far to go with technology also.
One day may be that this technology

15:07.920 --> 15:10.160
will become a big devil
and start killing us.

15:10.840 --> 15:18.080
Where have we reached with science also?
We have got hydrogen bomb, atomic bomb,

15:18.760 --> 15:22.920
then we are creating acid rain,
all kinds of problems.

15:22.920 --> 15:28.840
So the technology has no balance.
While the knowledge of the Spirit

15:29.440 --> 15:37.000
is not one-sided,
mental enterprises are only linear

15:37.000 --> 15:42.200
and they recoil on you.
But the spiritual enterprise

15:42.200 --> 15:46.560
is on all sides.
So it keeps complete balance

15:46.560 --> 15:47.880
and integration.

15:49.520 --> 15:57.040
So, what then, if I’m understanding,
is if we become spiritually enlightened,

15:57.040 --> 16:01.520
Self-realized as you call it,
even our planet will change

16:01.520 --> 16:05.160
and the disasters that we see
would lessen?

16:05.160 --> 16:08.440
Of course. All problems are created
by human beings only.

16:08.440 --> 16:16.720
The planet has created no problem.
So, if the human beings change, it will.

16:16.720 --> 16:19.960
And I think we don’t need
so many to change.

16:20.840 --> 16:28.880
Only some good people to change,
so they can influence others.

16:30.600 --> 16:33.320
What we need are leaders, good leaders.

16:34.880 --> 16:38.320
We’ve had some good leaders
here in America, Shri Mataji,

16:39.880 --> 16:43.720
certainly I think I’ve heard you mention
Abraham Lincoln.

16:43.720 --> 16:44.320
Of course.

16:44.320 --> 16:46.960
What were the qualities
that Abraham Lincoln had

16:46.960 --> 16:50.360
that we in America should try
and emulate more?

16:50.360 --> 16:53.480
He was an enlightened soul,
absolutely an enlightened soul

16:53.480 --> 16:58.600
in every way.
And how he lived collectively,

16:58.600 --> 17:03.760
he thought of collective.
The way he looked after

17:03.760 --> 17:07.800
all the sides of life,
that’s the sign of a Realized soul.

17:08.400 --> 17:12.080
But I don’t think now in America
they value him so much

17:12.080 --> 17:14.080
as they should have.
But one day,

17:14.080 --> 17:17.960
when they’ll be spiritually endowed,
they’ll value him very much.

17:17.960 --> 17:22.920
I saw a small little road somewhere
in New York in his name

17:22.920 --> 17:24.160
and I was surprised.

17:26.440 --> 17:29.520
Some school buildings also have his name,
Shri Mataji.

17:29.520 --> 17:31.680
Oh, I mean, you have to take a microscope
to see that.

17:34.000 --> 17:37.040
Shri Mataji, I think that’s one of the
problems here in America.

17:37.040 --> 17:43.160
We seem not to have the kinds of heroes
that we need to have,

17:43.160 --> 17:50.800
to give the role models.
But just getting away from America,

17:50.800 --> 17:57.600
and just looking on a global scope,
we see transformations

17:57.600 --> 18:02.680
in several countries.
China and India have reestablished ties.

18:02.680 --> 18:06.400
Soviet Union and America
have reestablished ties.

18:07.840 --> 18:12.520
Is there something going on globally
that is causing nations

18:12.520 --> 18:17.680
that we perceive to be imbalanced
to suddenly transform and become balanced?

18:19.360 --> 18:21.720
You see, now the communication
has improved

18:22.240 --> 18:27.000
and people see each other now
and everybody thinks others are better.

18:27.000 --> 18:30.680
Like Russians think Americans
are in the heavens

18:30.680 --> 18:33.800
and the Americans think that the Russians
are in the heavens.

18:34.320 --> 18:39.080
It’s not understanding.
When they are transforming,

18:39.080 --> 18:42.760
they should also see into what ditch
they are.

18:43.440 --> 18:45.760
They should find out
what problems there are.

18:46.320 --> 18:48.920
And when they are trying
to transform themselves,

18:48.920 --> 18:53.160
they should see that they don’t,
not fall into those ditches.

18:53.840 --> 18:58.480
Then only it will work out.
Otherwise, just copying somebody else

18:58.480 --> 19:02.280
or following somebody else,
it’s very artificial transformation

19:02.800 --> 19:04.560
and they will be in the same lurch.

19:05.560 --> 19:08.280
Well, that brings me
to the China’s situation,

19:08.280 --> 19:13.000
certainly there’s been massive
demonstrations for the past few weeks,

19:13.760 --> 19:17.680
where they’re looking to reform
to become more democratic.

19:18.680 --> 19:22.880
Is your implication that just adopting
our form of democracy

19:22.880 --> 19:24.600
is not China’s answer?

19:25.360 --> 19:28.480
Not at all.
There will be another ‘demonocracy’.

19:29.240 --> 19:31.600
Not at all.
I don’t think this kind of a democracy

19:31.600 --> 19:35.720
is of any use,
where there’s no sense of authority,

19:35.720 --> 19:41.320
there’s no sense of shame,
there’s no sense of

19:41.320 --> 19:46.280
collective understanding.
This kind of a democracy

19:46.280 --> 19:51.600
is not going to work out.
And Chinese think that you people

19:51.600 --> 19:54.480
have lots of money,
you have big, big cars

19:54.480 --> 19:57.200
and you have other things
of which you are fed up now.

19:58.720 --> 20:03.000
Otherwise, why should you take to drugs?
But they don’t see the other side of it.

20:04.440 --> 20:07.840
But I don’t say that what Chinese are,
they are all right.

20:08.720 --> 20:14.520
They all have to become ‘Sahaj’ to enjoy.
Then the whole political scene

20:14.520 --> 20:17.520
will change.
People will just think

20:17.520 --> 20:20.720
about the benevolence
and a balanced living.

20:22.160 --> 20:27.640
You’ve established Sahaj in 30 countries,
Shri Mataji.

20:30.200 --> 20:35.880
Tell me, besides India,
where all of us here in America realize

20:36.440 --> 20:40.280
the spiritual life
is of vast importance,

20:40.280 --> 20:44.240
is there another country that comes close
to the spiritual side

20:44.240 --> 20:45.480
that India portrays?

20:50.040 --> 20:54.040
I would say Turkey is very close
to India.

20:54.040 --> 21:00.480
So if you exclude Turkey,
then you can say Italy. Italy.

21:01.000 --> 21:06.400
Italian government, Italian people,
they’re very spiritually alert.

21:07.080 --> 21:08.760
They understand the spiritual person.

21:10.880 --> 21:15.000
And Americans, for example,
are not as sensitive?

21:15.840 --> 21:22.360
They are more sensitive to guru shopping.
If there’s somebody selling,

21:22.360 --> 21:25.600
then they are happy.
Here, if you are not selling,

21:25.600 --> 21:27.760
they are not happy.
You have to have Rolls Royce’s

21:27.760 --> 21:33.800
to impress them.
So with such kind of attitude,

21:33.800 --> 21:36.360
I don’t know how far I can go with them.

21:37.640 --> 21:43.680
Well, Shri Mataji,
you’re obviously very persistent

21:43.680 --> 21:47.600
because you’ve worked at this
for at least 20 years.

21:47.600 --> 21:53.120
Is there something that Americans can do
to become a bit more sensitive?

21:53.120 --> 21:58.600
I understand there’s a money orientation.
But is there something that we can do

21:58.600 --> 22:04.360
on a day-to-day life
to begin to understand the spiritual need?

22:05.480 --> 22:07.640
They have to see the shock
waiting for them.

22:08.520 --> 22:13.640
They have to see what problems there are,
and not to evade and glorify them.

22:14.640 --> 22:20.520
Whatever problems they have,
they make a big, big drama out of it,

22:20.520 --> 22:23.680
and think that something,
“This is very great”.

22:24.400 --> 22:28.120
So they should understand
that this was a mistake, this was wrong.

22:28.640 --> 22:33.520
Accept your mistakes and then understand
that this is not for your benevolence

22:33.520 --> 22:37.800
at all! It is for your destruction.
These are all destructive powers

22:38.440 --> 22:42.480
which are working within you,
because these are transitory things.

22:43.000 --> 22:46.480
And things which are transitory
are transitory

22:46.480 --> 22:49.600
because they have a built-in power
to get destroyed.

22:49.600 --> 22:54.520
Otherwise, why are they transitory?
So you have to seek the eternal.

22:56.560 --> 22:59.440
Shri Mataji, as you travel
through America,

22:59.440 --> 23:04.000
is there any state that’s more receptive
to your message than any other?

23:04.880 --> 23:07.480
Is there anywhere in America
that’s sensitive?

23:12.400 --> 23:15.520
I think San Diego is a good place,
San Diego.

23:15.520 --> 23:19.640
I went there before also.
First time I visited San Diego,

23:19.640 --> 23:25.960
there was a parapsychology institution.
And I told them that,

23:25.960 --> 23:28.920
“This is all very wrong,
it’s all negative forces.

23:28.920 --> 23:33.240
Don’t indulge into these things,
this is all black magic,

23:33.240 --> 23:35.680
this is not good”.
And they were very angry, of course.

23:35.680 --> 23:40.040
I mean, it was not very good of Me also,
because I was supposed to be their guest,

23:40.040 --> 23:42.160
and I shouldn’t tell them off.
But I didn’t know

23:42.160 --> 23:46.000
what parapsychology means.
Parapsychology actually,

23:46.000 --> 23:50.240
according to Sanskrit style,
‘para’ will be the ‘above’ psychology.

23:50.240 --> 23:54.680
But it was even below psychology.
So, I thought I should not mislead them

23:54.680 --> 23:57.520
and I must tell them frankly,
because I am a Mother

23:57.520 --> 24:01.280
and I shouldn’t tell them lies.
But now we find

24:01.280 --> 24:04.760
it’s all destroyed already.
People who were running it are destroyed.

24:05.280 --> 24:08.040
And those who were there,
they came back to Me

24:08.040 --> 24:11.960
and that’s why in, San Diego,
we have a better center.

24:12.520 --> 24:16.360
Maybe the sea is helping them,
I don’t know what is helping them.

24:16.360 --> 24:21.920
But San Diego is the best place, I think,
where today we find Sahaja Yogis

24:21.920 --> 24:22.960
developing better.

24:24.760 --> 24:29.320
Shri Mataji,
You’ve travelled certainly extensively

24:29.320 --> 24:33.960
and I should mention that
You’ve been married 45 years

24:33.960 --> 24:38.480
to a very prominent figure,
Mr. C.P. Srivastava,

24:38.480 --> 24:42.960
of the United Nations.
And I wonder, in your travels,

24:42.960 --> 24:47.800
I mean, we in America have such difficulty
juggling jobs and families

24:47.800 --> 24:52.200
and extracurricular activities.
How have you managed

24:52.200 --> 24:54.120
to have your marriage survive?

24:54.606 --> 25:00.360
Oh, we are very happily married.
You see, actually, I was a housewife,

25:00.360 --> 25:04.280
so I waited till my daughters got married.
And it all timed with it,

25:04.280 --> 25:07.520
that I discovered also
this en masse method,

25:07.520 --> 25:11.680
after my daughters were married.
I have two daughters.

25:12.320 --> 25:19.360
Then my husband also got elected
to this job by 134 nations.

25:19.360 --> 25:23.160
So, fortunately and unfortunately
he has to also travel a lot.

25:24.360 --> 25:29.520
And I have always given him all freedom
that he needed to travel,

25:29.520 --> 25:33.720
even before he came to London
on this job.

25:35.120 --> 25:40.320
So he realizes that it’s very important
work I am doing.

25:40.320 --> 25:46.720
He himself has said that,
“To transform one person is difficult.

25:46.720 --> 25:51.360
You have transformed so many people”.
He always used to say that,

25:51.360 --> 25:55.200
“You are something great,
but you can’t make others like you”.

25:55.200 --> 26:01.000
But now he says,
“My honesty compels me to admit

26:01.000 --> 26:05.400
that this is a tremendous work
and this will really create

26:06.800 --> 26:10.600
real united nations.
Because it will come from within”.

26:12.120 --> 26:15.360
So he’s been working
with the United Nations

26:15.360 --> 26:18.024
and sees your work as valuable
if not more.

26:18.024 --> 26:20.280
Yes, he’s the senior most
Secretary General now.

26:20.280 --> 26:22.480
He’s the senior most Secretary General,
my husband.

26:23.840 --> 26:26.360
And yet he finds your work
to be of great value.

26:26.360 --> 26:28.320
Of very great importance.

26:28.320 --> 26:32.200
Well, Shri Mataji, obviously,
in your vision,

26:32.200 --> 26:36.120
you see personal transformation,
people becoming healthy,

26:36.120 --> 26:39.800
people becoming well.
Nations growing

26:39.800 --> 26:44.160
and embracing other nations.
What’s the role of America

26:44.160 --> 26:46.520
in this global transformation?

26:46.520 --> 26:49.880
Very great.
America doesn’t know what

26:51.080 --> 26:57.040
is the role of America is.
America is the one which stands

26:57.040 --> 27:01.760
for collectivity.
It has to spread collectivity

27:01.760 --> 27:05.320
and communications.
It has the power of communications.

27:05.320 --> 27:07.560
All these technology
and all those things,

27:07.560 --> 27:15.120
have come to America for communication.
And communication is going to work out.

27:16.240 --> 27:19.040
So, all those false gurus
who have come to America

27:19.040 --> 27:23.120
suddenly become overnight,
well-known people in the whole world,

27:23.920 --> 27:30.520
because they have a big name in America.
Or the communication that we have

27:31.840 --> 27:37.800
through our talks, through our messages,
through our lectures,

27:37.800 --> 27:42.200
all these are very important.
And they have to guard themselves

27:42.200 --> 27:50.760
as to what they are talking about.
Also, they are very busy helping nations

27:51.480 --> 27:59.480
here and there, like Vietnam and Korea,
Nicaragua, all sorts of things.

28:01.040 --> 28:04.280
But the discrimination part,
which is very important

28:04.280 --> 28:07.240
for communication,
is slightly likely.

28:08.240 --> 28:15.160
If they knew how to discriminate,
they would be of the greatest help

28:15.160 --> 28:19.800
for the Divine work.
But this discrimination can only come

28:19.800 --> 28:22.080
after they have this transformation.

28:24.360 --> 28:29.360
Well, you spoke of a few good people
in America getting this transformation

28:29.360 --> 28:36.160
and then this discrimination.
Do you have hopes that this will

28:36.160 --> 28:38.760
take place in the next decade?

28:38.760 --> 28:43.320
It has to, I’m very hopeful.
America has to realize.

28:43.320 --> 28:48.480
It is coming to that point.
All these shocks of AIDS

28:48.480 --> 28:53.280
and shocks of this drug,
and all other problems,

28:53.280 --> 28:56.120
ecological problems,
all these are facing us today,

28:57.800 --> 29:02.240
are bringing us to a point
to see there’s something wrong somewhere.

29:04.360 --> 29:07.880
Many people are going back
to organised religions,

29:07.880 --> 29:12.120
those who are not involved
in the New Age.

29:13.440 --> 29:20.320
I hear in your talks you speak of Jesus.
You speak of Mohammed.

29:20.840 --> 29:27.680
You speak of Buddha and Krishna.
What is the essence of these teachings,

29:28.240 --> 29:33.640
that you feel, brings all of these
different prophets and holy people

29:33.640 --> 29:35.200
and incarnations together?

29:35.200 --> 29:41.160
The essence of their teaching was,
all of them said one thing,

29:41.160 --> 29:46.240
depending on the time that they came,
they might have given additional colour,

29:46.240 --> 29:52.040
additional forms.
But the essence was that,

29:53.040 --> 29:58.680
“Seek the eternal”.
And transitory is to be used,

29:58.680 --> 30:03.760
knowing that it is transitory,
into its own limitations.

30:06.080 --> 30:15.680
And the religions that are formed today,
are artificial religions.

30:15.680 --> 30:22.440
They are not innate religions,
which are based on these great prophets

30:22.440 --> 30:31.320
and great incarnations.
Because on a tree,

30:31.320 --> 30:37.360
there are lots of flowers.
At different times they come, bloom,

30:37.360 --> 30:44.480
give their fragrance.
These people have plucked these flowers,

30:46.320 --> 30:47.880
and which are dead.
And they say,

30:47.880 --> 30:50.320
“This is mine, this is mine,
this is mine”.

30:51.440 --> 30:57.360
That’s why it looks so funny.
They grew on the same sap of

30:57.360 --> 31:03.960
“Seek the eternal”, with genuineness.
Most of them are money oriented.

31:04.960 --> 31:10.280
It’s all a big business.
You cannot have business of Christ.

31:11.440 --> 31:15.880
You know how He took a hunter
and hid people who were doing business.

31:15.880 --> 31:17.720
And now what will He do if He comes?

31:19.440 --> 31:25.760
Is there any religion that we practice
that’s close to the type of idea

31:25.760 --> 31:27.560
or ideal that you have?

31:28.440 --> 31:33.280
So far, I haven’t seen any.
I haven’t seen anyone.

31:33.280 --> 31:36.520
That’s why the fundamentalists
who are going to religion

31:36.520 --> 31:42.080
will become Hitlers.
Because they are not with reality.

31:45.320 --> 31:51.840
Now we have a religion which we call as
the universal pure religion

31:51.840 --> 31:53.920
within ourselves,
and that is to be awakened.

31:55.480 --> 31:58.520
And this happens with the process
that you’ve discussed.

31:58.520 --> 32:03.240
Yes, when the Kundalini arises
and pierces through six centres,

32:03.240 --> 32:07.560
and you get the connection
with the Divine Power,

32:07.560 --> 32:13.280
and you establish the connection,
then you are that pure religion.

32:13.280 --> 32:15.360
You are not to be told,
“Don’t do this, don’t do that”.

32:15.360 --> 32:16.480
You just don’t do it.

32:18.920 --> 32:24.160
You’ve talked about it.
But I don’t know if I’ve asked you,

32:24.160 --> 32:29.440
how does this happen?
I mean, you said it’s spontaneous,

32:29.440 --> 32:34.560
but is it something that one needs
to go in their room and ask for it?

32:36.040 --> 32:39.560
Nothing of the kind.
If you just come to my program,

32:39.560 --> 32:42.920
I’ll work it out.
And then you can work it out.

32:42.920 --> 32:46.320
It’s very simple.
It’s like one enlightened light

32:46.320 --> 32:52.760
can enlighten another light.
One candle which is not yet enlightened

32:52.760 --> 32:55.360
cannot do it.
But another one does it.

32:55.360 --> 33:00.160
But there’s nothing special about it.
You see, how do you do it?

33:00.160 --> 33:04.240
Just like that.
Because it’s already there, it just works.

33:06.040 --> 33:12.960
Before we close, I wanted to ask
whether the vision that you’ve portrayed,

33:12.960 --> 33:19.680
which is extremely beautiful,
do you really think the world

33:19.680 --> 33:23.560
will achieve this peace
and transformation?

33:23.560 --> 33:26.520
Oh, I’m very sure,
very sure in my lifetime.

33:27.280 --> 33:31.120
I’m very sure now, in my lifetime,
it will work out.

33:32.440 --> 33:34.240
I want to thank you very much.

33:34.240 --> 33:35.680
May God bless you.
For coming, Shri Mataji.

33:35.680 --> 33:38.600
May God bless you. Thank you very much.
May God bless you. Thank you.

33:45.560 --> 33:46.440
Very natural.

33:53.560 --> 33:55.040
I acted well, I should say.

33:57.120 --> 33:58.080
And she kept me aligned.

33:59.080 --> 34:02.200
I had to kept her quite all right
on the line.

34:04.440 --> 34:06.120
I forgot to look at my papers.

34:10.640 --> 34:13.920
Shri Mataji, would you like to have food
in the ashram.

34:15.000 --> 34:18.080
I think if you go the ashram,
it would be better, because [unclear].

34:18.080 --> 34:19.360
All right, I can have food.

34:21.160 --> 34:22.640
Would you like to have it here
or in the ashram?
